title: MV多世界插件末地问题
author: mclingwu
txt_content:
末地只能进入一次从末地出来之后后台输出信息
World 'DIM1' was unloaded from memory.
把DIM1卸载了，有没有屌大的知道什么原因，或者MW和MV能不能一起用

replies.author: 弥猫うた
replies.txt_content:
服务器主目录cauldron.yml 文件
world-environment-settings:
  normal:
    keep-world-loaded: true
  nether:
    keep-world-loaded: true
  the_end:
    keep-world-loaded: false 改成true
